               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Maṣḥafa gǝnzat “Book of the Funeral Ritual” (fols. 3ra-113ra)&#xD;
- Introduction (fols. 3ra-5rb)&#xD;
- Discourse of St Athanasius on death (fols. 22rb-28rb)&#xD;
- Maṣḥaf za-wäḍʾat ʾǝm-ʾIyarusalem “Book that Came from Jerusalem” (fols. 28va-36vb)&#xD;
- Excerpt from Mawāśǝʾt (fols. 41ra-42ra; 61va-62va; 77ra)&#xD;
- Homily by St Jacob of Serug for the funeral of priests and deacons (fols. 82ra-85ra)&#xD;
- Homily by ʾabbā Salāmā, Metropolitan of Ethiopia (fols. 91vb-94rb)&#xD;
- Lǝfāfa ṣǝdq “Bandlet of Righteousness” (fols. 100ra-103rb)&#xD;
- Mangada samāy “Journey to Heaven” (fol. 103rb-103vb)&#xD;
&#xD;
Additio 1.</summary>
